torybook**\r\n _Dev checks_\r\n- [x] Confirm that prop table is populating \r\n- [ ] Take note of missing examples/stories (if any)\r\n\r\n**React package**\r\n _Dev checks_\r\n- [ ] Go to https://codesandbox.io/s/github/carbon-design-system/carbon/tree/main/packages/react/examples/codesandbox and confirm that you can use the component as expected from `@carbon/react` \r\n\r\n**Accessibility** \r\n _Dev checks_\r\n- [x] Confirm that there are no violations in Accessibility checker\r\n- [x] Confirm that component works as expected with VoiceOver\r\n\r\n**Migration docs**\r\n_Design and dev check_\r\n- [ ] Any breaking changes to this component are present in the v11 [migration guide](https://v11.carbondesignsystem.com/migrating/guide/overview).\r\n   - [x] Design\r\n   - [ ] Develop\r\n","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon/issues/10428/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon/issues/10428/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"score":1},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon/issues/10746","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon/issues/10746/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon/issues/10746/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon/issues/10746/events","html_url":"https://github.com/carbon-design-system/carbon/issues/10746","id":1137051804,"node_id":"I_kwDOBQ58z85Dxgic","number":10746,"title":"[Bug]: Radio button selected dot misalignment","user":{"login":"fabpico","id":4472725,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjQ0NzI3MjU=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/4472725?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/fabpico","html_url":"https://github.com/fa