e inputs themselves in vanilla HTML)\r\n- Try to submit form without selection\r\n\r\n### Code of Conduct\r\n\r\n- [X] I agree to follow this project's [Code of Conduct](https://github.com/carbon-design-system/carbon/blob/f555616971a03fd454c0f4daea184adf41fff05b/.github/CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md)\r\n- [X] I checked the [current issues](https://github.com/carbon-design-system/carbon/issues) for duplicate problems","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon/issues/10502/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon/issues/10502/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"score":1},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon/issues/6037","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon/issues/6037/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon/issues/6037/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon/issues/6037/events","html_url":"https://github.com/carbon-design-system/carbon/issues/6037","id":614166376,"node_id":"MDU6SXNzdWU2MTQxNjYzNzY=","number":6037,"title":"Adding className property to the radio of the radio button","user":{"login":"peterloveland","id":2086381,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjIwODYzODE=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/2086381?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/peterloveland","html_url":"https://github.com/peterloveland","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/peterloveland/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/peterloveland/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/peterloveland/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/peterloveland/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/peterloveland/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/peterloveland/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/peterloveland/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/peterloveland/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/peterloveland/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":true},"labels":[{"id":1056028593,"node_id":"MDU6TGFiZWwxMDU2MDI4NTkz","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon/labels/type:%20enhancement%20%F0%9F%92%A1","name":"type: enhancement üí°","color":"3ddbd9","default":false,"description":""}],"state":"open","locked":false,"assignee":null,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":1,"created_at":"2020-05-07T15:55:16Z","updated_at":"2020-05-07T18:06:55Z","closed_at":null,"author_association":"NONE","active_lock_reason":null,"body":"We've got a use case to provide 3 options, with radio buttons. 2 of these options have additional text inputs to enable our use case.\r\nWe've managed to get the following without any overrides to Carbon (just providing classNames and CSS to the right pieces) but are stuck with this alignment of the actual radio button:\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/2086381/81315718-90572580-9082-11ea-9158-01e889dfd679.png)\r\n\r\nIdeally we'd just like to be a able to add a property to the radio selector itself:\r\n`.bx--radio-button__appearance ${optional class here}`.\r\n\r\nIs there a more 'Carbon approved' way of handling this scenario? Or would it be possible to have this optional class plumbed in?\r\n\r\ncc. @matthew-chirgwin ","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon/issues/6037/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon/issues/6037/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"score":1},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-syste